Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅大人为何想从我们的保护之下逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身处的时间和空间都跟我们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人能了解她的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当她的保姆实在是当腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此 对我们来说 她是必不可缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 属下定会将她带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没什么时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白娜丝 我进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆带回来那个女孩子的病历
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗的时候有点在意 就去查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:00:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可不是一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(714,500)\pos(175,380)\fnSimSun\fs30}第三话 “千年的迷惑”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将这里称为掩体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩体？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口藏在群山之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有潜沙才能进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古人好像是将这里建成安全的避难场所了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆带回来的那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗的时候我查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,构成Theseus的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是经过完美设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为Ideal Children的克隆人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她的身体特征
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更接近我们拿度亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的事情 之前也碰到过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我医治的那个Theseus伤兵 他的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拿度亚的克隆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想到的结论只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应该是经过完美设计的IC克隆体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为反复的复制而劣化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能利用了我们拿度亚的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定那个女孩也...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩 可不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里遗留着当时的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的“古鱼”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}古鱼：第一集男主开的那台浮游沙上摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有能潜沙的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是在这里找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能启动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我有进行维护 随时都能开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我没骗你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我能不能开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等你好了 我教你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 想让你看的东西在其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 吓了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可以说是进行量子跃迁和逆操作的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将它——莫诺克洛斯打入到拟似相变立场去 就可以中和立场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然太深奥了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能把那沙鲸——OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关在沙里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们在追捕着OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 量子跃迁引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我哥哥让它们重新绽放光芒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在追捕OZMA的时候 他失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成它...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是个了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我长得多么高 也比不上他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能用它打倒OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就能看到哥哥的背影了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆 你回船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想问玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅 你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻你相当于是Theseus的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么要一个人驾驶着帆船逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theseus军在找我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们很快就会找到这里来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让你们再次陷入危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我也不知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了见你们称之为沙鲸的OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见OZMA？ 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我想回答 也没有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那千年的悠久时光中 我一直迷惑着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉一直在寻找着那份答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅累了 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是要治好身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回船上去吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 她的情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在医生在诊断中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能那么简单就有结果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明看起来才十几二十岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端粒居然这么短
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}端粒：染色体末端的DNA重复序列
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天额外加菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家尽情吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要大吃一顿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从地狱转了一圈回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上天堂之前 吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞开吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 昨天真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 差点就被蒸熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theseus那些家伙 为什么盯上我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是因为精力旺盛的小朋友带回来的那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人 给巴鲁丹诺斯带来了厄运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 索留 你刚才说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在谈论了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你带回来的是可怕的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 精力旺盛的小朋友就这点能耐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们有必要去帮他一把
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是久违的美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我参战！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩 我们也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我在吃饭中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起鸡皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅 你看到那个女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚转个身 她就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙 给我安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆 玛雅溜出医务室 不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我在船内找了一遍 但没看到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我能不能开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等你好了 我教你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅对沙上摩托感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那种沙摩...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到掩体去的话 可以找到几台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打算穿过环礁 逃到沙漠中去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么想要逃离我们
