Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是正确的 什么是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么对议案进行表决
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多数赞成 议案通过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是为了我们能继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为这颗星球的盟主进行长久的统治
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真魁梧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基多大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言下之意 您是看中这个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们IC 拥有最完美的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而存在于世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学的缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就在于它能让人类丧失尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"心脏"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到那里的话 未来应该就会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你见面 说不定能明白一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回船上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅身体 想穿过沙海简直就是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需逃避 巴鲁丹诺斯会接受你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就是你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁丹诺斯是所有人的家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不想让大家再次陷入危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是OZMA吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 要"保护"拿度亚少年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备射击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那少年是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不允许有人加害于他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把玛雅还给我 假面混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我跟你没完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把玛雅大人带回舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 基多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 拜托 帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰前方2000 出现巨大的拟似相变立场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙贼的潜沙舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 范围太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆 萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快将玛雅大人带回舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎比他哥哥还要贼运亨通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆打算独自去救玛雅回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 有Theseus的最新型潜沙舰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 这样一来就是沙中的全面对决了
